Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:01:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're undertaking this four-way Battle Royale in order to determine the match-ups in the Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, I know you want to face that worthless deadbeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I will not allow such scrutiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your awaiting fate is to fight {\b0}me{\b1} in the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to ensure this, I have to get rid of the annoying deadbeat and Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you better get ready to Duel me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Their Respected Opponents"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Dark Jeroid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy also has a Special Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment it is Summoned, one Monster on the field has their Attack Power decreased by 800 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now... Which Monster should I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come attack me, Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And fall victim to my Trap...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment you do, Destruction Ring will leave your Life Points practically dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Trap, is it? It's written all over his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well let's see... His Majesty's Gilfer Demon has 2200 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with Dark Jeroid's Special Ability, he'll only drop from 2200 Attack to 1400.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still 200 Attack Points higher than Dark Jeroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I think it's rather obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go after Jounouchi's Gearfried!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Jeroid's Special Ability activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gearfried's Attack Power drops by 800 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fooled ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna lower your Monster's Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! This man depends on luck too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut yer trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It rolled a two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Dark Jeroid loses half it's Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for {\i1}you{\i0}, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your{\i0} Monster's the dead one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Sword of Gearfried!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This can't be...!\N His body's shrinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just activated my reverse card, Shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Magic Card cuts the Attack Power of the selected Monster in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, your Gearfried's Attack shrank to a low 800!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Jeroid destroys Gearfried!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, Kaiba!\N Why'd you go and butt in...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that damn Kaiba had something up his sleeve...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize he was {\i1}this{\i0} low a bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just part of the game's strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kaiba-kun still has two set cards on the field. They can't let their guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my big brother!\N He activated his reverse card right in the pits of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All enemies that oppose me serve only one purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make me {\i1}win{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what was dat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get worked up, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's going to save you, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, I'm by your side, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That way my brother can focus on Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep it up, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are the other players' positions this turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba has two reverse cards out on the field.\N And Blade Knight in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik has no reverse cards, but he does have his Dark Jeroid in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} has just one reverse card...\N He's clearly at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it? What the hell are ya all starin' at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Who gives a damn\N if my field is empty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Gilfer Demon is the strongest Monster on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what's bothering me are those reverse cards Kaiba set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They must be Traps.\N I can't carelessly attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who should I aim for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's my only target!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:07:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi must be thinking of his promise to fight Jounouchi in order to become a True Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's gonna hit Malik or Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s got his eyes focused in only one pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been staring at Malik the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Jounouchi's been aiming for Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to save Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} with his own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}will{\b1} save Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll save her with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a Duelist just like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...just like she fought alongside us up until now... I really want to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She saved my butt a ton of times, when I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}That's{\b1} for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oi! What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu, don't tell Yugi this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:08:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two of us promised to fight each other fair and square the day we become True Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True Duelists?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be honest, I'm not sure if I'll be able to call myself that, even after all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's one thing I do know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can't save Mai with my strength alone, I'm not qualified to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So in order to keep\N my promised with Yugi, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll beat the hell out of Malik with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'll rescue Mai from her suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...? He said all that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} would say, alright... Just like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks it's his fault that he couldn't protect Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack with Gilfer Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster I target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you do that, Yugi...\N I wanted to ask you what a {\i1}True{\i0} Duelist is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack with Gilfer Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster I target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... I wanted to ask you what a {\i1}True{\i0} Duelist is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is now a good time\N for him to be asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I {\i1}do{\i0} know one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}True{\i0} Duelist wouldn't go and interrupt someone else's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for the answer through all of Battle City, and made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, it's because I wanted to fight you fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With each guy I fought in the city, I got a little closer to the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More like the answer a deadbeat found on the path to mediocrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... Because of you, I don't back down from any opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me to never give up, no matter how strong the opponent is, and to trust in my cards all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys taught me about the strength of trust, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's gotten into you all of a sudden...?\N You're freaking me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And all the Duelists I fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been a while, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you finally showed yourself, Insector Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was looking forward to meeting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attack, my Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Queen's Hell Breath!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haga, this match is over already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trap Card, activate! Graverobber!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Graverobber, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup. And the card I'm taking from your Graveyard is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ya see, I really can't stand bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! Insect Queen is done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fortress Whale is fried to a crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I play the Magic Card Revival of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I revive a Monster this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong?! Now hurry and come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all that boasting you did before, show me how you fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't afford to lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have my sea to fight against!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't give up until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, I can't let this card stay in the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't just stare! Now come and get me, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all showed me my own {\i1}weaknesses{\i0} I didn't know I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've helped me to {\i1}grow{\i0} as a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai! Your opponent's not decided yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter {\b0}who{\b1} my opponent is, I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next time we meet, it'll be in the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi, I'm not a soft Duelist like you who needs another's power to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were damn right about that, Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You taught me\N something important, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only {\i1}one{\i0} person can win Battle City and gain victorious glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Battle Royale!\N We're {\i1}all{\i0} your enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored to {\i1}tears{\i0} over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get on with the\N goddamn Duel already!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! If you're a True Duelist, take down your enemy! Take down {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing favorites just so you can keep your promise with me in the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the weakest one here in the current situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look around you and you'll see that I'm the one with no reverse cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun may have more Life Points at the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One attack from Gilfer Demon would send him close to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a basic strategy of this game to take down the weakest guys first, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your next turn!\N Just attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I lose this match, I'll still get to the Final and fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you {\i1}believe{\i0} in me, {\i1}attack{\i0} me... Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}, this is your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now I can't take Red-Eyes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}, I'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take care of your Red-Eyes until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mhm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's face each other in the Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack, Gilfer Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\N Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gilfer Flame!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself, Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you down with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai... I'll save you,\N no matter what it takes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's almost out of Life...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did you do this for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have the time to stand around staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You better win! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those tears for your little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope it shines with a bright light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai! I'll get your light back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Axe Raider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to attack Malik...? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy {\i1}I'm{\i0} attacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going after {\i1}Kaiba{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he after {\i1}Malik{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?\N Doesn't he want to save Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he change his attack target so far into the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or did he just bluff his wanting to attack Malik so he could go after Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!\N You really {\i1}are{\i0} a nobody, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:17:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna beat {\i1}himself{\i0} while trying to beat {\i1}my{\i0} big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Axe Raider! Attack Blade Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it, deadbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba's got a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take{\i1} this{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurricane Cutter!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction Ring!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Destruction Ring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster the Destruction Ring attaches to is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Monster's Attack Points are taken out of the controller's Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no desire to blow up alongside this common deadbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate my face-down Instant Quick-Play Magic Card, Defense Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It negates all damage\N inflicted by a Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! This time it's {\i1}really{\i0} game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means Jounouchi's Life Points are at zero...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Called it! Jounouchi's the one who lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:17:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My{\i0} Life hit zero...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activated Graverobber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graverobber is a card that steals one card from the opponent's Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now if ya don't mind, Malik-{\i1\b0}chan{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking that Spell of Pain you tossed in the Graveyard off your hands for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using this card, I can transfer all damage I receive to another player!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn good work, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like you to turn your enemy's strength against himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get things done when you put your mind to it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good thinking, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he had attacked Dark Jeroid with Axe Raider,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik would have only taken 500 points of damage to his Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But by attacking Kaiba and making use of his Trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then using Graverobber at just the right moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he was able to activate Spell of Pain and take Malik down in one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was an excellent strategy, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later~!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to deeply regret this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now Malik's in the first round of the Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Jounouchi's got no Monsters, reverse cards, or {\i1}anything{\i0} for that matter out on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think's gonna happen next turn when my brother goes to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. My field's {\i1}wide{\i0} open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I planned though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you {\i1}planned{\i0}, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me {\i1}laugh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a loser like {\i1}you{\i0} who relies on nothing but {\i1}luck{\i0} had any sort of plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Knight! Direct Attack Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet in the Final, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Battle Royale was nothing more than a game to decide our opponents in the Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Sorry to keep ya waitin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to sleep in darkness as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm kickin' {\i1}your{\i0} ass, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duels for the Semi-Finals has just been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First match of the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik Ishtar versus Katsuya Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second match!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou versus Seto Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel was fated, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}... Wait for me in the battlefield of the Final round!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to be there after I settle things with Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Gate, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally headed to the battlefield of the final matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may as well refer to it as a gateway to a world of {\i1}darkness{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling yourself! Even with that Ra card of yours, I'm gonna beat you to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us head to the final stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch the gondolas!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik's fighting Jounouchi in the first round of the Battle City Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want him to win so Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} will wake up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's facing one of the God Cards, The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} knows of Ra's terrifying abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way for Jounouchi to fight against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik just activated a Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Semi-Final Match of Darkness: Jounouchi VS Malik"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:23:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
